The paper discusses a web application that uses machine learning techniques to help researchers explore and discover scientific publications. The application includes personalized content-based article recommendations and an advanced full-text search. These features suggest that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
